title: fanoutqa: Who is the mayor of each of the sixth to ninth most populous cities currently in the United States? (3d5d3d43bae31b4b)

chat_history.content: Who is the mayor of each of the sixth to ninth most populous cities currently in the United States?

Here is the mayor of the sixth to ninth most populous cities in the United States, in order:

1. Phoenix, Arizona — Kate Gallego
2. Philadelphia, Pennsylvania — Kenneth Brannon
3. San Antonio, Texas — Ron Nirenberg
4. San Diego, California — Todd Gloria.

functions.name: delegate
functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.

instructions.description: Detailed instructions on what your helper should do to help you.
